OL,3,CPolling stations open as Scots elect
OL,4,Cnew Holyrood Parliament
OL,6,FPolling stations across Scotland have
OL,7,Fopened as the country elects a new
OL,8,Fbatch of MSPs to Holyrood.
OL,10,FVoters have until 10pm on Thursday to
OL,11,Fcast their ballot in a contest that
OL,12,Fwill decide who Scotland's MSPs will
OL,13,Fbe ` as well as determining who will
OL,14,Fbe first minister.
OL,16,FA total of 129 seats in the Scottish
OL,17,FParliament are up for grabs, with
OL,18,Fvoters electing 73 constituency
OL,19,Frepresentatives, with a further 56
OL,20,FMSPs elected via eight regional lists.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
