PN,35402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1778186660
OL,3,CPolling stations open as Scots elect
OL,4,Cnew Holyrood Parliament
OL,6,FUnlike previous elections ` other than
OL,7,F2021 because of the Covid-19 pandemic
OL,8,F` votes will be counted on Friday
OL,9,Frather than overnight, with the final
OL,10,Fresult likely to be known by late
OL,11,FFriday evening.
OL,13,FCampaigners have spent the past six
OL,14,Fweeks traversing the country in the
OL,15,Fhopes of winning the keys to Bute
OL,16,FHouse.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
