PN,35403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1778186660
OL,3,CPolling stations open as Scots elect
OL,4,Cnew Holyrood Parliament
OL,6,FFirst Minister John Swinney's SNP has
OL,7,Fled the polls since the beginning of
OL,8,Fthe campaign, with Mr Swinney telling
OL,9,Fvoters a majority for his party ` a
OL,10,Frarity in the Holyrood voting system `
OL,11,Fwill allow him to put more pressure on
OL,12,FWestminster to grant a second
OL,13,Freferendum on independence.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
