PN,35404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1778186660
OL,3,CPolling stations open as Scots elect
OL,4,Cnew Holyrood Parliament
OL,6,FSpeaking ahead of polls opening, Mr
OL,7,FSwinney said the election was
OL,8,F"Scotland's opportunity to choose a
OL,9,Fbetter future by voting SNP for real
OL,10,Faction on the cost of living, to lock
OL,11,FNigel Farage out of power, and to
OL,12,Fsecure a fresh start with
OL,13,Findependence".
OL,15,FHe added: "By casting both votes for
OL,16,Fthe SNP, Scotland can elect a strong
OL,17,Fmajority SNP government that will
OL,18,Falways stand up for Scotland,
OL,19,Fprioritise the cost of living, and
OL,20,Fdeliver that fresh start of
OL,21,Findependence that Scotland needs."
OL,26,@pD@AOUuD@MO]wD@KOU}D@bO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
