OL,3,CPolling stations open as Scots elect
OL,4,Cnew Holyrood Parliament
OL,6,FSNP Westminster leader Stephen Flynn `
OL,7,Fwho is running for Holyrood at this
OL,8,Felection ` said the ballot offered
OL,9,Fpeople to prosect of the "fresh start
OL,10,Fof independence".
OL,12,FMr Flynn said: "The increasingly
OL,13,Funaffordable cost of living in the UK
OL,14,Fhas defined this election. Brexit
OL,15,FBritain is broken ` and Scotland is
OL,16,Ftrapped in a never-ending cycle of
OL,17,Fsoaring bills and constant chaos under
OL,18,FWestminster control.
OL,26,@qD@ZOUrD@PO]tD@POU
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1778186660
OL,3,CPolling stations open as Scots elect
OL,4,Cnew Holyrood Parliament
OL,6,F"The fresh start of independence is
OL,7,Fthe opportunity Scotland can't afford
OL,8,Fto miss. It is the opportunity to use
OL,9,FScotland's huge energy wealth to lower
OL,10,Fhousehold bills and build a better
OL,11,Ffuture ` but it will only happen if
OL,12,Fpeople unite behind the SNP today.
OL,14,F"Every vote for the SNP will count to
OL,15,Fdeliver the strongest possible support
OL,16,Fwith the cost of living now ` and to
OL,17,Fescape the constant chaos of
OL,18,FWestminster control with independence."
OL,20,FOne of the unknowns ahead of Friday's
OL,21,Fresults is the fate of Reform UK.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUzD@gO]
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
