PN,35410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1778186660
OL,3,CPolling stations open as Scots elect
OL,4,Cnew Holyrood Parliament
OL,6,FMeanwhile, forecasts suggest the
OL,7,FScottish Tories' recent history of
OL,8,Fdefying political gravity ` initially
OL,9,Fengineered by former leader Baroness
OL,10,FRuth Davidson ` which saw them grasp
OL,11,Fthe unionist vote in Scotland and sit
OL,12,Fin second place for the past decade
OL,13,Fcould be over, with Russell Findlay's
OL,14,Fparty projected to shed votes and
OL,15,Fseats.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
