FL,355,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F354A1778186660
OL,3,CPolling stations open as Scots elect
OL,4,Cnew Holyrood Parliament
OL,6,FThe campaign has been dominated by the
OL,7,Fcost of living, with the SNP pledging
OL,8,Fto cap bus fares and prices of
OL,9,Fsupermarket essentials while Reform
OL,10,Fand the Scottish Tories have honed in
OL,11,Fon tax cuts.
OL,13,FScottish Labour has also pitched tax
OL,14,Fcuts, but only if an Anas Sarwar-led
OL,15,Fgovernment can kickstart the economy.
OL,17,FThe Scottish Greens have pledged to
OL,18,Fintroduce more taxes, which would pay
OL,19,Ffor universal free bus travel.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
